<date when="1900-07-18">July 18, 1900</date>.
<title level="a">OUR IMMIGRATION.</title></bibl>
   </div>
  </front>
  <body>
   <p>Since we have a census- that is for 120 years, the Germans have furnished the largest number and even to-day this nationality shown the highest percentage of immigrants, as may be ascertained from the following table, the result of two censuses:-</p>
